  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had very mixed feelings, but the thing that attracted me was that as a management consultant, I needed to get a wider aspect of practical management, not only just in the United Kingdom, and Germany had been extremely successful to build itself up again after the War to a large extent through its management and its approach to-- to-- to complex situations.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I felt I could learn a lot over there which would stand me in good stead later on when I came back to the United Kingdom.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And ostensibly, I was supposed to go there for a year, but this extended to two years, to three years, and 3 and 1/2 years.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then finally, I got back here by sheer luck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A British, large engineering company, a steel plant in Sheffield, was very interested to see what this American organization was doing in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were quite impressed, and they said we'd like to do the same thing here in the UK, but could we do it with Steve?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were over there for three days, and they saw what I was doing there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I acted as an interpreter as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we came to Sheffield, and this is where we still are today, you see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But before you came to Sheffield, how did you actually feel about being back in Germany, the country from which you'd fled?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was difficult at first, but ultimately, I found that there were a lot of people-- there were of course, this happened in the late-- early '60s, 1960, '65, round about that time.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
